Updated EZSTATE storage architecture.

This patch adds 4 essential JSONAdapted classes to facilitate
the storage of the Appointment class and the 3 coupled
classes of Date, From, To.

The implementation is rather straightforward, using the same
structure as JsonAdaptedPerson and JsonAdapatedTag to
ensure that the deserialization process from JSON to
a usable Model class occurs as intended.

Additionally, the corresponding JsonAdaptedPersonTest and
JsonSerializableAddressBookTest have been updated, including
typicalPersonsAddressBook.json and
duplicatePersonAddressBook.json.

commitResults.messageBody:
An issue I found is that when users need help with certain commands, they have to read through the entire user guide which
may be cumbersome.

Henceforth, I introduce a simple chat bot that allows users to get useful responses for their queries efficiently. For now, the
chat bot only accommodates to very trivial queries but will be further developed on when the other developers submit their
finalised command classes and their respective formatting.
